        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">If you want to bitch about an easy epic then bitch about the monk epic.  After you get your RotWF it takes literally 1 day to kill the boss mobs.</P><P>It's not very tough at all.  My guild did 95% of the epic quest in a single day for our primary monk.  The cleric one is also a piece of cake for the most part.  </P><P>So before you start crying about how easy the necro one is now, try checking those ones out first.</P><P>Personally I'm in a guild that is deemed as 'semi decent' but I don't think we have the fire power for the 2nd floor of Hate.  Nor for the bosses in Fear.</P><P>So I doubt it'll be all that common on necros.  Yeah the high level necros you see around now who are in kick ass guilds will probably score it, but that's all you'll see for the time being.</P><P>Just my 2 cents worth.</P><P><BR>-----------<BR>Excessum Letum, Iksar Necro<BR><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=70030" target="_blank">http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=70030</a></P><P>Officer of The Corps<BR>A Veeshan Guild<BR><a href="http://www.sixohfour.com/corps" target="_blank">http://www.sixohfour.com/corps</a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
